    <h1>Send response</h1>

    <p>To communicate with the requester, use the <a href="../../list-of-windows/alvao-webapp/requests">Requests</a> - <strong>Reply to requester</strong> command, which responds to the last message received from the requester, or sent to the requester as part of the request.</p>
    <p>If you want to reply to a specific message in the request communication (<a href="../../list-of-windows/alvao-webapp/requests/request">Request</a> - <em>Communications</em> tab) use the command in the menu of that message - <strong>Reply</strong>.</p>


